On tomorrow's CBS Evening News, American innovation,

00:19:44.24 --> 00:19:46.64
how a Tennessee middle school is dealing with the growing

00:19:46.64 --> 00:19:47.87
teacher shortage.

00:19:47.87 --> 00:19:49.41
And a reminder, if you watch us live,

00:19:49.41 --> 00:19:51.80
set your DVR so you can watch us later.

00:19:51.80 --> 00:19:54.12
I hope you have a Happy Valentine's Day.

00:19:54.12 --> 00:19:55.95
I'm Norah O'Donnell in our nation's capital.

00:19:55.95 --> 00:19:57.55
Good night.

